1. *Pomerio* sam stolicu da bih uzeo svoj džemper. (I moved the chair to take my jumper.)

2. *Pomeram* svoje stvari u novi stan. (I'm moving my things to a new apartment.)

3. On *pomeri* stolicu da bi se bolje video. (He moved the chair to get a better view.)

4. Ona *pomeri* stolicu bliže prozoru. (She moved the chair closer to the window.)

5. *Pomerite* stolice u krug da možemo svi da sedimo zajedno. (Move the chairs in a circle so we can all sit together.)

6. *Pomeren* je zid za još jednu fotografiju. (The wall was moved to make room for one more picture.)